RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

95-1222. Byrnes v. LCI Communication Holdings Co.

Franklin App. Nos. 94APE09-1372 and 94APE09-1396. Reported at 77 Ohio St.3d 125, 672 N.E.2d 145. On motion for reconsideration and on motion of Ohio Chapter of the National Organization for Women et al. for leave to file motion for reconsideration. Motions denied.

Resnick and Pfeifer, JJ., dissent.
